== Incidents ==
On 26 July 2015, a male passenger on Shenzhen Airlines flight ZH9648 from Taizhou to Guangzhou attempted to set fire to the aircraft cabin before being overpowered by the aircrew and other passengers. 95 passengers and 9 crew were evacuated; two passengers were injured. The aircrew were later awarded for their actions, while two passengers were given .

